org.rakiura.cpn
Interface NetVisitor

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
NetVisitorAdapter, XMLSerializer
public interface NetVisitor
extends java.io.Serializable

Utility for network analysis and graph traversal. This is based on the object oriented switch, and follows strictly the Visitor design pattern. Appropriate nodes of the net, i.e. in particular places, transitions, but also arcs will call appropriate methods from this interface.
